// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0260 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 363ce28c-b999-5c08-abde-8179c648ef24

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
